After Issuance: Sokcho Dongwha Room Management Team

735
00:58:25,310 --> 00:58:27,030
Why would he get moved all of a sudden?

736
00:58:27,030 --> 00:58:29,060
Is Kim Jin Hyeok getting kicked out to Sokcho?

737
00:58:29,060 --> 00:58:32,520
This... Would the CEO know?

